		<title>Apple invests $1 billion in Chinese ride-hailing service Didi Chuxing</title>

		<title>Bangladesh heist linked to attack on Sony: BAE researchers</title>


		<description>NEW YORK (Reuters) - Malicious software used in February's $81 million heist at Bangladesh Bank is linked to other cyber attacks, including the high-profile 2014 attack on Sony's Hollywood studio, according to a new report from cyber security firm BAE Systems.<div class="feedflare">

		<title>Apple falls below $90 as iPhone worries fester</title>
